      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5132-Choose-Your-Attitude.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Choose Your Attitude&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Choose Your Attitude 
    &lt;div id=&#34;choose-your-attitude&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#choose-your-attitude&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The world around us is either a warfield or playground.  &lt;br&gt;
If it is warfield then we keep fighting.  &lt;br&gt;
If it is a playground, then we keep playing.  &lt;br&gt;
If we are interested in doing karma then  &lt;br&gt;
these are two kinds of Karma options before us.  &lt;br&gt;
In one karma one gets exhausted and wants to quit,  &lt;br&gt;
in another one enjoys and wants to continue the game.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
